    "author_channel_id": "UCIxmZ8oehSrDgR0yKsM0SgQ",
    "text": "The ADO A20 was free to you, a folding bike can do the same job if you had to use your own money. If you had a removalble front wheel, you could squeeze a regular bike in your car. Is there no public transit in Cantebury?",
    "likes": 1,
    "published_at": "2021-11-17T18:45:22Z",
    "reply_count": 2,
