        "author": "@ThinkingandTinkering",
        "author_channel_id": "UC4AkVj-qnJxNtKuz3rkq16A",
        "text": "Yes it was - something I made clear in the first video in this playlist. A folding bike can't do the same job - a 'normal' folding bike needs leg power to move it - this is pedal assist great for old guys like me. The same goes for removing a front wheel with the added trouble of removing the front wheel then putting it back on. Of course there is public transport but it is inconvenient, still a walk away and takes ages. But, we all make our choices don't we?",
        "likes": 2,
        "published_at": "2021-11-17T18:54:45Z"
